WEBVTT

00:00.080 --> 00:01.942
Previously on Andi Mack...

00:01.967 --> 00:03.636
You're the shooting guard
for the Monarchs.

00:03.660 --> 00:05.429
We could really use a shooting guard.

00:05.463 --> 00:07.231
Please, join the team?

00:07.792 --> 00:10.234
Denied! At least try next time.

00:10.267 --> 00:13.304
You were right. This team is a hot mess.

00:14.157 --> 00:16.660
- I can't have you on the team.
- What a joke.

00:17.138 --> 00:19.714
- What were you guys talking about?
- I can't do a somersault, okay?

00:19.738 --> 00:22.641
You can't do a somersault?
I can help you with that.

00:24.190 --> 00:26.894
I came to congratulate you
on your engagement.

00:26.927 --> 00:28.728
- Thank you.
- I just wish my relationship

00:28.762 --> 00:31.163
with Morgan's father
was more like yours.

00:31.196 --> 00:32.980
I never saw it coming.

00:33.005 --> 00:35.409
For six years, we had
a pretty perfect relationship.

00:35.434 --> 00:38.237
- And then?
- And then, we got married.

00:38.270 --> 00:40.606
- Are these wedding invitations?
- Yeah.

00:40.639 --> 00:42.218
You know, this is
my favorite part of the job,

00:42.242 --> 00:44.678
when someone's life
is gonna change forever.

00:44.711 --> 00:46.346
- Um...
- Wait! What?

00:46.379 --> 00:48.782
I don't think I'm gonna mail
these out today after all.

00:48.815 --> 00:49.822
Is that Jonah?

00:49.847 --> 00:52.219
I'm really glad he's had
Amber to confide in.

00:52.251 --> 00:54.888
I can't believe I thought they
were actually back together.

00:59.090 --> 01:01.028
Anyone else feel like
their eyes are burning?

01:05.274 --> 01:07.176
- Whoa.
- Yeah.

01:07.209 --> 01:09.980
We all saw that? That just happened?

01:11.848 --> 01:13.983
He's coming over. Uh, act natural.

01:14.016 --> 01:17.655
- I don't remember how.
- No, we need answers.

01:19.388 --> 01:21.024
Hey! Jonah!

01:22.491 --> 01:25.228
Would it kill her
to mind her own business?

01:29.903 --> 01:30.938
Hey, guys.

01:30.965 --> 01:32.703
- Jonah!
- Joey Bee!

01:32.705 --> 01:34.941
- Anything you want to tell us?
- Huh?

01:34.974 --> 01:37.277
- We just saw you with Amber.
- What happened with Libby?

01:37.310 --> 01:38.912
Do you have two girlfriends?

01:38.944 --> 01:40.247
Not cool, Beck.

01:40.280 --> 01:42.849
- We thought Amber was your friend.
- Well, she is.

01:42.882 --> 01:44.827
And that she was helping
you through a tough time.

01:44.851 --> 01:46.854
- She was.
- With kissing?

01:46.887 --> 01:48.610
Okay, okay. I'm not being a jerk.

01:49.488 --> 01:52.359
- Libby and I broke up.
- When?

01:53.325 --> 01:56.129
- A couple days ago.
- Why didn't you tell us?

01:56.385 --> 01:59.500
I was embarrassed. She broke up with me.

01:59.768 --> 02:02.170
And you're already back with Amber?

02:02.202 --> 02:04.365
- Amber?
- It just happened.

02:06.141 --> 02:08.143
I'll catch you guys later.

02:10.077 --> 02:12.713
Maybe it'll be different
for him this time around.

02:12.747 --> 02:14.083
Amber's changed a lot.

02:15.088 --> 02:16.217
You're welcome.

02:16.250 --> 02:20.588
Hmm. And as the next ex in the lineup,

02:20.622 --> 02:23.691
- you're on deck.
- Nope. Not it.

02:23.725 --> 02:25.427
Mack out.

